title: Wayne Rooney at 30 - watch the story of his record-breaking career
text:
Wayne Rooney at 30 - watch the story of his record-breaking career 
Irish Examiner Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Wayne Rooney made his footballing debut at the tender of age of 16. 
His astonishing career – which has seen him score more than 300 goals in almost 700 games for Everton, Man United and England – has earned him a legendary status in the sporting world. 
As Rooney turns 30, we’ve taken a look back at the record-breaking moments which have defined his career.
